Description
This dataset was produced from US economic time series data available from
https://fred.stlouisfed.org/. economics is in "wide"
format, economics_long is in "long" format.
title: US economic time series

parameters.uempmed:
median duration of unemployment, in weeks,
https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/UEMPMED
parameters.pce:
personal consumption expenditures, in billions of dollars,
https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PCE
